MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1204778523}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8b1bcd2fa329bad4d87512daf004a187, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::StoryController
  storyText: {fileID: 2000162631}
  storyLines:
  - 'My kind was wiped out long ago...


    (Press any key or mouse click to continue) '
  - 'None of us survived, not even me... '
  - How am I talking, you ask? Well...
  - 'The parts of me that remained... my fossils... they were preserved. '
  - 'I was reawakened... revived. But I was no longer on the planet I once knew. '
  - 'I found myself in this mad world, being experimented on by some hideous creatures...
    the very same beings who brought life back into me... only me. '
  - Yes, I am the last of my kind. But I wish to escape from this horrific world,
    to free myself from the prison I have been subjected to in this second life.
  - 'Now is the time. '
